{"tid":1806974,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"前線手足入，最新2020 勇武注意事項","createTime":"2020-01-01T14:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T09:16:59.000Z","uid":10133,"like":30,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd0bc1cdcdf97d9ab50194431c6af1558a6c597","tid":1806974,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1</span>, 不能帶背囊，與攝衫同理。因為黑警用短槍，收埋喺背囊，帶背囊即係有機會有槍，就係鬼！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6S0A1S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6S0A1S.jpg&h=974709d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pq5Nf1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpq5Nf1T.jpg&h=e4d88cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2</span>, 不能大隻有肌肉，似狗。最好好似下圖咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7eBTPt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7eBTPt.jpg&h=728b286a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3</span>, 頭髮不能剪太短，雖然短髮方便上軍咀，但似狗，所以都不能！最好好似下圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvYZRBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvYZRBN.jpg&h=ef91ecd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4</span>, 要攝衫，與1 同理，因為黑警試過放手槍喺腰間。雖然黑警可以放槍入背囊，但都要攝！著住件褸都要攝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攝完無撚用都要攝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5, 不能用單邊耳機，不能用單邊耳機聽住抗爭頻道/ zello 同隊友聯絡。狗先用單邊耳機！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n違反以上條例，將會被<del>手足</del>影大頭篤灰！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉鬼萬歲！割佢老母席！</span></span>"},{"pid":"dad35efb3de8d66d167ca76559f679a35ab0e995","tid":1806974,"uid":93649,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"睇到第2屌左出聲 唔好ON9啦"},{"pid":"926efa85b0636d0d92972bdaacfa44f3759b3158","tid":1806974,"uid":10133,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"本人被捉鬼師，經驗豐富，有咩問題歡迎問本大師。"},{"pid":"11165b8efd7276e07bed3092398676d9c56632c2","tid":1806974,"uid":191246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:53:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24d343d017ec6b660a6b7e6fc99c55fdb1ec468d","tid":1806974,"uid":10133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dad35efb3de8d66d167ca76559f679a35ab0e995","tid":1806974,"uid":93649,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"睇到第2屌左出聲 唔好ON9啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港，捉鬼革命！"},{"pid":"3eeb2e549f8ac8fce6fe56a478bdcaf2541f8cd3","tid":1806974,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:55:07.000Z","msg":"9小陣喇 拉"},{"pid":"82939fbe4c7887267bb6f86dc1efedce16f94583","tid":1806974,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"第二張圖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90eb3b24921b79c8312f928a765c20599b014c5a","tid":1806974,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"勇武要瘦柴，大隻就捉你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdee360adce691f70abf8bcac50b61099f1145a9","tid":1806974,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:59:41.000Z","msg":"捉鬼撚幫幫手，留喺屋企咪上街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a61b355547c74b8770b67ed27f59294130e78e","tid":1806974,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82939fbe4c7887267bb6f86dc1efedce16f94583","tid":1806974,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"第二張圖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji